        "setup": "Create/register a StubHub application following the [Authentication docs](https://developer.stubhub.com/docs/authentication/). Use the app's `client_id` and `client_secret` to obtain tokens from `https://account.stubhub.com/oauth2/token` for production or `https://sandbox.account.stubhub.com/oauth2/token` for sandbox. For user-authorized access, redirect users to `https://account.stubhub.com/authorize` with your registered HTTPS `redirect_uri`; for app-only access, use the client-credentials flow described in [Application-Only Authentication Flow](https://developer.stubhub.com/docs/authentication/application-only-authentication-flow)."
